import React from 'react'

export const CloseSvg = () => (
    <svg width='24' height='24' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'>
        <path d='M3 21L21.0001 2.99895' stroke='currentColor' strokeWidth='1.5' strokeLinecap='round'/>
        <path d='M3 3L21 21' stroke='currentColor' strokeWidth='1.5' strokeLinecap='round'/>
    </svg>
)

export const CloseMiniSvg = () => (
    <svg width='24' height='24' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'>
        <path d='M15.9958 8.00366L8.00415 15.9953' stroke='currentColor' strokeWidth='1.5' strokeLinecap='round'
              strokeLinejoin='round'/>
        <path d='M15.9983 16L8 8' stroke='currentColor' strokeWidth='1.5' strokeLinecap='round' strokeLinejoin='round'/>
    </svg>
)

export const CloseCircleSvg = () => (
    <svg width='16' height='16' viewBox='0 0 16 16' fill='none' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'>
        <path
            d='M8.00016 14.6666C11.6668 14.6666 14.6668 11.6666 14.6668 7.99998C14.6668 4.33331 11.6668 1.33331 8.00016 1.33331C4.3335 1.33331 1.3335 4.33331 1.3335 7.99998C1.3335 11.6666 4.3335 14.6666 8.00016 14.6666Z'
            stroke='currentColor' strokeLinecap='round' strokeLinejoin='round'/>
        <path d='M6.11328 9.88668L9.88661 6.11334' stroke='currentColor' strokeLinecap='round' strokeLinejoin='round'/>
        <path d='M9.88661 9.88668L6.11328 6.11334' stroke='currentColor' strokeLinecap='round' strokeLinejoin='round'/>
    </svg>
)
